comment._content: The [New York] sun., February 06, 1915, Page 11, bottom of column 1 chroniclingamerica.loc.gov/lccn/sn83030272/1915-02-06/ed-... Indicates that "Little Miss Muffet" won several second prizes at the "Bustanoby Tea Show." But this picture is probably of a different dog show. The sun., October 31, 1915, Second Section Sporting and Automobiles, Page 18, column 1 chroniclingamerica.loc.gov/lccn/sn83030272/1915-10-31/ed-... Suggests (a) that Mrs. Henry Hill had other dogs she showed and (b) that dog shows were frequent..
